---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Best Shopify Email Apps for B2B Wholesale in 2026';
const description = 'Compare Shopify email apps for B2B wholesale stores by account segmentation, reorder workflows, pricing context, source links, and practical tradeoffs.';
const apps = [['Sequenzy','Lean teams running account nurture','Focused sequence workflows','Validate wholesale-specific integrations','https://sequenzy.com/'],['Klaviyo','Large account and product-interest segments','Rich profile and event logic','Needs disciplined account data and governance','https://www.klaviyo.com/features/segmentation'],['Omnisend','Wholesale promotions and coordinated SMS','Accessible campaign automation','Less suited to complex account approval logic','https://www.omnisend.com/features/marketing-automation/'],['Drip','Commerce teams tracking repeat orders','Ecommerce event automation and reporting','May exceed a small wholesale operation','https://www.drip.com/features'],['Brevo','Marketing plus transactional account messages','Broad messaging and contact options','More manual account modeling','https://www.brevo.com/features/marketing-automation/'],['Shopify Email','Small wholesale stores sending basic updates','Native product and customer setup','Limited account-role branching','https://www.shopify.com/email-marketing'],['Mailchimp','Wholesale newsletters and product-line announcements','Familiar campaign and audience tools','Approval and account logic may need integration','https://mailchimp.com/features/marketing-automation/'],['ActiveCampaign','Wholesale journeys tied to CRM and sales ownership','Flexible automation and handoffs','More setup and seat governance','https://www.activecampaign.com/marketing-automation'],['Sendlane','DTC-to-wholesale teams using commerce behavior','Behavioral automation and reporting','Review account and catalog integration support','https://www.sendlane.com/'],['Customer.io','Wholesale programs with detailed account events','Flexible event-triggered messaging','Requires clean account and role data','https://customer.io/'],['Privy','Smaller sellers capturing qualified wholesale interest','Forms and lightweight campaigns','Not a full account-management system','https://www.privy.com/'],['Postmark','Invoices, order, and account-status notifications','Reliable transactional delivery','Not a promotional wholesale platform','https://postmarkapp.com/'],['Resend','Developer-led wholesale stores with custom account events','Simple API-first delivery','Engineering owns roles, routing, and suppression','https://resend.com/']];
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}><main class="container page-stack"><p class="eyebrow">Shopify email apps</p><h1>{title}</h1><p class="lede">Wholesale email is account communication, not just consumer promotion. Buyers may need line-sheet updates, reorder prompts, inventory context, payment guidance, and messages tailored to their business relationship.</p><p>We prioritize explicit account fields, product and order signals, suppression rules, and measurable reorder journeys. Confirm current pricing and integration limits from official sources before rollout.</p><h2>Shortlist for wholesale operations</h2><table><thead><tr><th>App</th><th>Best fit</th><th>First workflow</th><th>Tradeoff</th></tr></thead><tbody>{apps.map(a=><tr><td>{a[0]}</td><td>{a[1]}</td><td>{a[0]==='Klaviyo'?'Account and category onboarding':a[0]==='Omnisend'?'Wholesale launch campaign':a[0]==='Sequenzy'?'Buyer reorder sequence':a[0]==='Drip'?'Account repeat-order path':'Transactional account updates'}</td><td>{a[3]}</td></tr>)}</tbody></table>{apps.map(a=><section><h2>{a[0]} for B2B wholesale</h2><p><strong>Best for:</strong> {a[1]}. {a[0]} is useful when the store distinguishes a buyer’s account, role, region, and purchasing history. Do not use a consumer discount flow for an account that needs negotiated pricing or human approval.</p><p><strong>Why it stands out:</strong> {a[2]}. Start with one account-safe journey—such as a reorder reminder or product-line update—and measure qualified replies, repeat orders, and unsubscribes. The outcome should be judged against the wholesale sales process, not a generic ecommerce benchmark.</p><table><tbody><tr><th>Pros</th><td>{a[2]}; supports a focused account test; can use Shopify order behavior.</td></tr><tr><th>Cons</th><td>{a[3]}; integration, seats, and contact volume affect cost.</td></tr><tr><th>Pricing context</th><td>Verify official pricing for contacts, sends, seats, SMS, and integrations.</td></tr><tr><th>Source</th><td><a href={a[4]} rel="nofollow">Official product information</a></td></tr></tbody></table></section>)}<h2>Decision guide</h2><table><thead><tr><th>Priority</th><th>Start with</th><th>Reason</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Many account and product signals</td><td>Klaviyo</td><td>Flexible segmentation.</td></tr><tr><td>Lean buyer sequences</td><td>Sequenzy</td><td>Focused workflows reduce operating overhead.</td></tr><tr><td>Repeat-order analysis</td><td>Drip</td><td>Commerce-oriented reporting fits reorder programs.</td></tr></tbody></table><p>See the <a href="/shopify-email">Shopify email overview</a>, <a href="/alternatives">alternatives library</a>, and <a href="/for/b2b-wholesale">B2B category guide</a>.</p></main></BaseLayout>
